Overview

This dashboard shows Authentication overview related to the Prisma Access Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested authentication logs from Prisma Access.

It displays authentication events categorized by protocol, server, and user. It also highlights the top security policy rules and source IPs. Additionally, it provides essential details.
